data.description: Attention Investors, flippers, renovators and contractors! High and Dry Acre+ with Solid 3/1 home freshly painted in pleasing, soft palette with stone and reclaimed wood features throughout. New Water Heater & New Roof installed in 2023 after Hurricane Ian. Lovely front sun porch wraps around to side covered porch with rear stairs. South side has chain-link fenced area off Living Room side porch perfect for a garden or dog/chicken run. Bathroom has been totally redone in beautiful floor-to-ceiling subway tile for easy maintenance with a custom tiled floor & shower. Large, spacious bedrooms too! Laundry area off kitchen. Hwy 17 frontage Zoned A-10, perfect for opening your Farmstand or Greenhouse/Plant Nursery for your home-based Ag business! Owner is selling as-is and will make no further repairs. COME and SEE and Make an Offer soon!
